        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer31020991" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15232117258400384250">I am almost finished with this one, and I have loved it. What a fascinating look into the middle ages and into one of the most interesting couples in history. I am biased toward Heloise and champion her ability to speak her mind to the man she loved, married, and became an abbess to please.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


